<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM6.7.9">
<l>āṟum piṟaiyu maravamu maṭampuñ caṭaimē laṇintaṭalam</l>
<l>nīṟum pūci yēṟūru miṟaiyōṉ ceṉṟu kuṟaiyirappa</l>
<l>māṟoṉ ṟillā vācanīr varaimār vakalat taḷittukantāṉ</l>
<l>nāṟum poḻilcūḻn taḻakāya naṟaiyūr niṉṟa nampiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>When the god, who rides a bull, having smeared ash on [his] body,</l>
<l rend="indent">adorning on [his] matted locks</l>
<l>A river, the crescent moon, serpents, and cassia flowers,</l>
<l rend="indent">came and begged in want,</l>
<l>He who was pleased, having granted fragrant water from the breadth</l>
<l rend="indent">of his mountain[-like] chest without any blemish,</l>
<l>Is the noble who stands in Naṟaiyūr, which becomes beautiful</l>
<l rend="indent">being encircled by fragrant groves.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
